title: White House says Obama will raise cyber concern with China's Xi
text:
15 White House says Obama will raise cyber concern with China's Xi 
Reuters: President Barack Obama will raise concerns about cyber security with Chinese President Xi Jinping when they meet in Washington this month amid rising U.S. worries about Chinese hacking of U.S. government and commercial targets, the White House said on Monday.
